{"tid":2229052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[又準備走數?]美國農業部長：無法確定中國能否兌現農產品的採購承諾","createTime":"2020-10-04T06:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T06:12:31.000Z","uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d60abff728be0c12d9da07492d6980b814995ced","tid":2229052,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>路透社說，<strong><span class=\"red\">中國承諾今年進口價值365億美元的美國農產品</span></strong>，但今年上半年的採購數額嚴重欠缺，讓人懷疑中國是否能夠落實對美中貿易協議的承諾，實現將美國農產品的採購水平在2017年的基礎上增加50%的目標。<br />\n<br />\n報導援引美國農業部的統計數據說，<strong><span class=\"red\">中國今年1月到7月進口的美國農產品只有86億美元</span></strong>。但中國8月份和9月份提高了美國農產品的進口速度，一共進口了大約1200萬噸的大豆和400萬噸的玉米。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-unsure-of-china-commitment-10022020/5606972.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fus-unsure-of-china-commitment-10022020%2F5606972.html&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wilwEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=dce0b420\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/us-unsure-of-china-commitment-10022020/5606972.html</a>"},{"pid":"0c2792154c4b3b124f566e5b0e39b269135c9660","tid":2229052,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5af6e73f55f422673aa231bab8a61a060bd00386","tid":2229052,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e06e8e62447c77417c4cece7315375a85f90c516","tid":2229052,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T06:12:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}